,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',44,'en','download_user_app_title','Complete Multipurpose eBusiness Solution',NULL,NULL),(66,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',45,'en','download_user_app_sub_title','loteat is a Laravel and Flutter Framework-based multi-vendor food, grocery, eCommerce, parcel, and pharmacy delivery system. It has six modules to cover all your business function',NULL,NULL),(67,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',50,'en','earning_seller_title','Become a Seller',NULL,NULL),(68,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',51,'en','earning_seller_sub_title','Register as seller & open shop in 6amMart to start your business',NULL,NULL),(69,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',52,'en','earning_seller_button_name','Register',NULL,NULL),(70,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',54,'en','earning_dm_title','Become a $Delivery Man$',NULL,NULL),(71,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',55,'en','earning_dm_sub_title','Register as delivery man and earn money',NULL,NULL),(72,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',56,'en','earning_dm_button_name','Register',NULL,NULL),(73,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',93,'en','terms_and_conditions','<h1>Loteat Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Last Updated: January 2026</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Loteat (the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;). The Platform is operated by <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>. Please read these Terms &amp; Conditions carefully before using the Platform. By accessing or using the Platform, you agree to be bound by these Terms.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>1. Platform Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform Name: Loteat<br />\r\nCompany Name: FLYREACH LIMITED<br />\r\nRegistered Address: FLAT 2304, 23/F HO KING, COMM CENTRE, 2-16 FA YUEN STREET, MONG KOK, HONG KONG<br />\r\nPhone: +852 63573049<br />\r\nEmail: contact@loteat.com</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>2. Platform Nature</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Loteat is a global instant retail and delivery platform designed to provide users with convenient and efficient online ordering and delivery services. Users may browse products, place orders, and enjoy instant or same-day delivery services through the Platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform integrates digital systems to provide comprehensive services including product display, order processing, payment settlement, and customer support.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>3. Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform provides users with services including but not limited to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Product information display and search</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Online ordering and order management</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Online payment and transaction support</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery status tracking and notifications</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Customer service and after-sales support</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform reserves the right to optimize, adjust, or upgrade the services according to operational needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>4. Orders and Transactions</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Users shall carefully review product details, quantities, prices, and delivery information before placing an order. Once an order is confirmed, it shall be deemed as the user&rsquo;s true intent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If an order cannot be completed due to inventory changes, system issues, or force majeure, the Platform will notify the user and assist with refunds or alternative solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>5. Delivery and Time Estimates</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery times displayed on the Platform are reasonable estimates based on historical data and real-time conditions and are provided for reference only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform will make reasonable commercial efforts to ensure delivery efficiency. However, delivery times may be affected under special circumstances, including but not limited to severe weather, traffic control, or system maintenance.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>6. User Responsibilities and Conduct</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Users shall comply with the following rules when using the Platform:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Provide true, accurate, and complete personal information</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Not engage in any illegal, fraudulent, or infringing activities</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Not place malicious orders, conduct fake transactions, or abuse promotions</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Not disrupt or interfere with the normal operation of the Platform</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform reserves the right to take actions including warnings, functional restrictions, suspension, or termination of accounts for any violations.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>7. Account Security</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Users are responsible for safeguarding their account credentials and shall bear responsibility for all activities conducted under their accounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If any unauthorized use is discovered, users shall immediately notify the Platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>8. Refunds and After-Sales</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Users may request after-sales support through the Platform&rsquo;s customer service channels. The Platform will assist in handling refunds, replacements, or other reasonable resolutions where applicable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Refund amounts and processing methods shall be subject to the Platform&rsquo;s policies and the payment service providers.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>9. Intellectual Property</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>All content on the Platform, including but not limited to text, images, logos, interface designs, and system programs, are owned by the Platform or relevant rights holders and are protected by applicable laws.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No content may be copied, distributed, or used for commercial purposes without prior written permission.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>10. Force Majeure</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform shall not be liable for service interruptions or failures caused by force majeure events, including but not limited to natural disasters, war, epidemics, government actions, or network failures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform will make reasonable efforts to minimize the impact on users.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>11. Amendments</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform reserves the right to modify these Terms at any time in accordance with legal or operational requirements. Updated Terms shall take effect upon publication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Continued use of the Platform constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>12. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any disputes arising from these Terms shall be resolved through amicable negotiation. If negotiation fails, the dispute shall be submitted to the courts of Hong Kong with proper jurisdiction.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>13. Final Provisions</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If any provision of these Terms is deemed invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The final interpretation of these Terms belongs to <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>.</p>',NULL,NULL),(74,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',94,'en','privacy_policy','<h1>Loteat Privacy Policy</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Last Updated: January 2026</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>Loteat</strong> (the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;) collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information. The Platform is operated by <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By accessing or using the Platform, you agree to the collection and use of your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>1. Company Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform Name: Loteat<br />\r\nCompany Name: FLYREACH LIMITED<br />\r\nRegistered Address: FLAT 2304, 23/F HO KING, COMM CENTRE, 2-16 FA YUEN STREET, MONG KOK, HONG KONG<br />\r\nPhone: +852 63573049<br />\r\nEmail: contact@loteat.com</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We may collect the following types of information when you use the Platform:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2.1 Personal Information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Name</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Phone number</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Email address</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery address</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Payment-related information (processed via third-party payment providers)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>2.2 Technical Information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>IP address</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Device type and operating system</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Browser type</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Access time and usage logs</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>2.3 Order Information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Products ordered</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Order history</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Transaction records</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery status</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We collect and use your information for the following purposes:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To provide and operate the Platform services</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To process orders and payments</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To deliver products and services</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To communicate with users regarding orders or support requests</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To improve user experience and platform performance</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To comply with legal and regulatory requirements</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We may share your information with:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Payment service providers</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery and logistics partners</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Customer service providers</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Regulatory or legal authorities when required by law</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We do not sell or rent your personal data to any third parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, loss, misuse, or alteration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, no system is completely secure. You acknowledge that data transmission over the internet may carry inherent risks.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We may use cookies or similar technologies to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Remember user preferences</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Analyze traffic and usage behavior</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Improve platform functionality</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Users may choose to disable cookies through their browser settings, but this may affect certain features of the Platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>7. Data Retention</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>8. User Rights</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on applicable laws, users may have the right to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Access their personal data</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Request correction of inaccurate data</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Request deletion of personal data</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Withdraw consent for data processing</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Requests can be submitted via: <strong>contact@loteat.com</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of such external sites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Users are advised to review the privacy policies of those websites separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>10. Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Platform is not intended for users under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If we become aware that personal data of a minor has been collected, we will take reasonable steps to delete such information.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be published on the Platform and become effective immediately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Continued use of the Platform constitutes acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>12. Contact Us</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: contact@loteat.com<br />\r\nPhone: +852 63573049</p>',NULL,NULL),(75,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',95,'en','about_us','<h1>About Us | Loteat</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Loteat</strong> is a global instant retail and delivery platform dedicated to providing users with convenient, efficient, and reliable online ordering and delivery experiences through digital technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe that time is one of the most valuable resources in modern life. With the core philosophy of &ldquo;Faster, Simpler, Smarter&rdquo;, Loteat integrates advanced system architecture and intelligent operations to enable users to place orders quickly and enjoy hour-level or same-day delivery services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By continuously optimizing product experience and service processes, Loteat covers a wide range of everyday consumption scenarios, including daily essentials and instant local needs, helping users save time and improve overall life efficiency.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loteat is operated by <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>, headquartered in Hong Kong and serving users worldwide. We are committed to a user-centric approach, investing in technology innovation and service excellence to build a trusted global instant retail brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the future, Loteat will continue to expand its service coverage, enhance delivery capabilities, and bring smarter and more efficient instant retail solutions to more cities and regions around the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>Company Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Company Name: FLYREACH LIMITED<br />\r\nRegistered Address: FLAT 2304, 23/F HO KING, COMM CENTRE, 2-16 FA YUEN STREET, MONG KONG, HONG KONG<br />\r\nPhone: +852 63573049<br />\r\nEmail: contact@loteat.com</p>',NULL,NULL),(76,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',96,'en','about_title','About Us',NULL,NULL),(77,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',33,'en','refund_policy','<h1>Loteat Refund Policy</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Last Updated: January 2026</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Refund Policy is designed to protect the legitimate rights of users. By using Loteat (the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;), you agree to this Refund Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>1. Refund Eligibility</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Users may request a refund if their order cannot be fulfilled due to product unavailability, duplicate payment, system errors, or other platform-related issues.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Orders that have already been shipped or delivered are generally not eligible for a refund, unless there is a clear product quality issue or platform responsibility.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Refund requests must be submitted within 7 days after the order is completed. Requests submitted after this period will not be accepted.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>2. Refund Process</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Users can submit a refund request through the Platform&rsquo;s customer service or online application channel, providing order details and relevant supporting information.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform will review the request within 3-5 business days to determine whether it meets the refund eligibility criteria.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Approved refunds will be processed using the original payment method. The time it takes for funds to appear in your account may vary depending on the payment provider.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>3. Refund Amount</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The refund amount will be based on the actual payment made by the user and does not include any discounts, coupons, points, or promotional value used.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Any fees charged by the payment provider may be borne by the Platform or the user, depending on the payment method. The Platform reserves the right to adjust the refund amount within the scope permitted by law.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>4. Special Circumstances</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>In cases where orders cannot be fulfilled due to force majeure events, the Platform will make reasonable efforts to assist users with refunds or reordering.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform is not responsible for issues arising from inaccurate user information, such as incorrect shipping addresses, but will assist in order adjustments where feasible.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>5. Final Interpretation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The final interpretation of this Refund Policy belongs to <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>.</p>',NULL,NULL),(78,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',97,'en','cancellation_policy','<h1>Loteat Order Cancellation Policy</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Last Updated: January 2026</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Order Cancellation Policy explains the rules and procedures for canceling orders placed on <strong>Loteat</strong> (the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;). By using the Platform, you agree to this policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>1. Cancellation Eligibility</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Users may request to cancel an order <strong>before it has been prepared for dispatch or assigned for delivery</strong>.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Orders that have already been prepared, dispatched, or are out for delivery <strong>cannot be canceled</strong> through the Platform.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Cancellation requests must be submitted through the Platform&rsquo;s order management or customer service channels as soon as possible.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>2. Cancellation Process</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>To cancel an order, users should submit a cancellation request via the Platform&rsquo;s app, website, or customer service.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform will confirm the cancellation within 1-2 business days and provide a notification to the user.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>If the order is eligible for cancellation, any payments already made will be processed for refund according to the <strong>Refund Policy</strong>.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>3. Cancellation Fees</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Orders canceled <strong>before preparation or dispatch</strong> will not incur any cancellation fees.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Orders that cannot be canceled due to being prepared or dispatched may be subject to <strong>delivery or service charges</strong>, which will be deducted from any eligible refund.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform reserves the right to adjust cancellation fees in accordance with operational costs and applicable law.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>4. Special Circumstances</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>In the event of system errors, duplicate orders, or other platform-related issues, the Platform will review the situation and may allow cancellations outside the standard rules.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Force majeure events (such as natural disasters, traffic restrictions, or unforeseen emergencies) may affect order cancellations. The Platform will handle such cases reasonably and communicate with the user promptly.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>5. Final Interpretation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The final interpretation of this Order Cancellation Policy belongs to <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>.</p>',NULL,NULL),(79,'App\\Models\\DataSetting',98,'en','shipping_policy','<h1>Loteat Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Last Updated: January 2026</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy explains how orders placed on <strong>Loteat</strong> (the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;) are processed and delivered. By using the Platform, you agree to this policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>1. Delivery Service</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Loteat provides instant and same-day delivery services where available.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery times displayed on the Platform are <strong>estimates</strong> based on system data, logistics capacity, and real-time conditions, and are provided for reference only.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery services may vary depending on location, product type, and availability.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>2. Order Processing</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Once an order is confirmed, the Platform forwards it to the relevant fulfillment and delivery partners for processing.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform strives to process all orders promptly to meet estimated delivery times.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Orders placed outside operational hours or during high-demand periods may experience extended processing times.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>3. Delivery Charges</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery fees, if any, will be displayed at the time of order confirmation.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Any applicable taxes or surcharges related to delivery will be included in the final order price.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform reserves the right to adjust delivery fees in accordance with operational costs or regional regulations.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>4. Delivery Issues</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Users must provide accurate and complete delivery information.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Loteat is not responsible for delays or delivery failures caused by inaccurate user information, traffic conditions, extreme weather, or force majeure events.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>In case of lost, damaged, or incorrect deliveries, users should contact customer service immediately. The Platform will review each case and provide appropriate assistance or compensation according to applicable policies.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>5. Special Circumstances</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Delivery times may be affected by factors beyond the Platform&rsquo;s control, including natural disasters, traffic restrictions, public holidays, or system maintenance.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Platform will make reasonable efforts to inform users of significant delays and provide solutions such as rescheduling or refunds where applicable.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>6. Final Interpretation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The final interpretation of this Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy belongs to <strong>FLYREACH LIMITED</strong>.</p>',NULL,NULL);
